# CardXC.online — Cursor Rules

## Project
- Gift card marketplace (crypto-to-gift-card)
- Frontend: React + Vite + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS
- Backend: Node.js + Express (server/ folder)
- Deploy: Cloudflare Workers (frontend), Hostinger VPS (backend API)

## Architecture
- Frontend SPA deployed as Cloudflare Worker (auto-deploy on git push)
- Backend API at api.cardxc.online (VPS: 76.13.28.186, PM2)
- Database: PostgreSQL 16
- CDN: Cloudflare

## Style
- Dark theme (bg-[#0a0a0f], lime-green accents #a3e635)
- Tailwind CSS utility classes
- Remix Icon for icons
- Inter font family

## Rules
- Always use TypeScript strict mode
- Use Tailwind — no inline styles
- Keep dark theme consistent across all pages
- API routes in server/routes/
- Pages in src/pages/
- Components in src/components/ or page-level components/

## Deploy
- One command: `./deploy-all.sh "commit message"`
- Frontend: git push → Cloudflare auto-build
- Backend: rsync + PM2 restart on VPS

## Security Headers
- CSP, HSTS, X-Frame-Options configured in public/_headers
- Do not remove or weaken security headers
